on), and the action is logged (audit). If something goes wrong, you know who did what and when."]}],["$","br","4",{}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["When an AI agent deploys code, that entire chain breaks. The agent authenticated as... itself? Who authorized the deployment? Where's the proof?"]}],["$","br","6",{}],["$","h2","7",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Introducing Execution Warrants"}],["$","br","8",{}],["$","p","9",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["A warrant is a cryptographically signed authorization token with four properties:"]}],["$","br","10",{}],["$","p","11",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["1. ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Scope"}]," — exactly what the agent is allowed to do"]}],["$","p","12",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["2. ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Time-to-live"}]," — when the warrant expires"]}],["$","p","13",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["3. ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Issuer"}]," — who or what approved the action"]}],["$","p","14",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["4. ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Constraints"}]," — parameter bounds the execution must respect"]}],["$","br","15",{}],["$","p","16",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["Here's what one looks like:"]}],["$","br","17",{}],["$","div","18",{"className":"bg-navy-800 border border-navy-700 rounded-lg p-4 my-4 font-mono text-sm text-slate-300 overflow-x-auto","children":"json"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["{"]}],["$","p","20",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"warrant_id\": \"wrt-7f3a2b1c-...\","]}],["$","p","21",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"scope\": {"]}],["$","p","22",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"action\": \"deploy_service\","]}],["$","p","23",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"target\": \"api-gateway-prod\","]}],["$","p","24",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"parameters\": {"]}],["$","p","25",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"version\": \"2.4.1\","]}],["$","p","26",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"strategy\": \"rolling\""]}],["$","p","27",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["}"]}],["$","p","28",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["},"]}],["$","p","29",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"ttl\": 300,"]}],["$","p","30",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"issued_at\": \"2026-03-25T14:00:00Z\","]}],["$","p","31",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"expires_at\": \"2026-03-25T14:05:00Z\","]}],["$","p","32",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"issuer\": {"]}],["$","p","33",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"type\": \"operator\","]}],["$","p","34",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"id\": \"jane.smith\""]}],["$","p","35",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["},"]}],["$","p","36",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"constraints\": {"]}],["$","p","37",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"max_retries\": 1,"]}],["$","p","38",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"rollback_on_failure\": true,"]}],["$","p","39",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"affected_services\": [\"api-gateway\"]"]}],["$","p","40",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["},"]}],["$","p","41",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["\"signature\": \"0x7f3a...b2c1\""]}],["$","p","42",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["}"]}],["$","div","43",{"className":"bg-navy-800 border border-navy-700 rounded-lg p-4 my-4 font-mono text-sm text-slate-300 overflow-x-auto","children":""}],["$","br","44",{}],["$","h2","45",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"How It Works in Practice"}],["$","br","46",{}],["$","p","47",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Step 1: Agent proposes an action."}]," The agent submits an intent (e.g., \"restart the API gateway\") to the Intent Gateway."]}],["$","br","48",{}],["$","p","49",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Step 2: Policy Engine evaluates."}]," Is this action allowed? What risk tier is it? Does it require approval?"]}],["$","br","50",{}],["$","p","51",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Step 3: Approval (if required)."}]," T1/T2 actions wait for operator approval. T0 actions auto-approve."]}],["$","br","52",{}],["$","p","53",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Step 4: Warrant issued."}]," The Warrant Authority creates a signed warrant with specific scope and TTL."]}],["$","br","54",{}],["$","p","55",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Step 5: Execution."}]," The Execution Router uses the warrant to authorize the action. No valid warrant = no execution."]}],["$","br","56",{}],["$","p","57",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Step 6: Verification."}]," Post-execution, the Verification Engine confirms the actual execution matched the warrant scope. Did the agent restart *only* the API gateway? Did it use rolling deployment? Any deviation flags an alert."]}],["$","br","58",{}],["$","p","59",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Step 7: Audit."}]," Everything — the intent, policy decision, warrant, execution result, and verification — is recorded in the append-only ledger."]}],["$","br","60",{}],["$","h2","61",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Why Not Just Use RBAC?"}],["$","br","62",{}],["$","p","63",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["Role-based access control (RBAC) tells you *what an agent can do in general*. Warrants tell you *what an agent is authorized to do right now, for this specific action*."]}],["$","br","64",{}],["$","p","65",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["An agent might have the *capability* to restart services (RBAC). But for each restart, it still needs a *warrant* — a specific, time-limited, auditable authorization. This is the difference between \"you have a driver's license\" and \"you are authorized to drive this specific car, on this route, for the next 30 minutes.\""]}],["$","br","66",{}],["$","h2","67",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"The Legal Analogy"}],["$","br","68",{}],["$","p","69",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["This isn't accidental. The warrant concept borrows from legal systems intentionally. A police warrant must be:"]}],["$","li","70",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Specific (what can be searched)"}],["$","li","71",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Time-limited (when it's valid)"}],["$","li","72",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Issued by an authority (a judge)"}],["$","li","73",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Documented (on record)"}],["$","br","74",{}],["$","p","75",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["AI execution warrants follow the same principles. This isn't just good engineering — it's the kind of framework regulators understand and trust."]}],["$","br","76",{}],["$","h2","77",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"What This Enables"}],["$","br","78",{}],["$","li","79",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Compliance proof.** Show auditors exactly who authorized what, when, and why."}],["$","li","80",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Forensic analysis.** When something goes wrong, trace the full chain from intent to execution."}],["$","li","81",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Automatic containment.** Expired or scope-violated warrants automatically halt execution."}],["$","li","82",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Insurance evidence.** Demonstrate to cyber insurers that AI actions are governed."}],["$","br","83",{}],["$","hr","84",{"className":"border-navy-700 my-8"}],["$","br","85",{}],["$","p","86",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"Learn more about Vienna OS warrants in our documentation →"}],["$","br","87",{}]]}],["$","$L10",null,{"slug":"cryptographic-warrants-explained"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt